Name: REQUIRED TOTAL
Explanation: ENTER THE TOTAL QUANTITY OF AN ITEM REQUIRED TO BE HELD ON-HAND AND IN RESERVE BY A FORMATION/UNIT TO MEET THE NATO ASSIGNED TASK IN ACCORDANCE WITH FORCE STANDARDS OR ESTABLISHED MISSION REQUIREMENTS. QUANTITIES AS DECLARED BY NATIONS IN THE DPQ REPLY, WHEN APPLICABLE, OR AS DECLARED FOR NATIONAL UNITS IN PLANS/OPERATIONS. ENTER THE CONTEXT QUANTITY (0-99999999), FOR EXAMPLE "150".

Name: REQUIRED ON HAND
Explanation: ENTER THE QUANTITY OF AN ITEM REQUIRED TO BE HELD ON-HAND BY A FORMATION/UNIT (NOT INCLUDING ITEMS IN RESERVE) IN ACCORDANCE WITH FORCE STANDARDS/TASK REQUIREMENTS. ENTER THE CONTEXT QUANTITY (0-99999999), FOR EXAMPLE "110".

Name: TOTAL DUE IN
Explanation: ENTER THE QUANTITY OF ITEMS EXPECTED TO BE RECEIVED BY FORMATION/UNIT BEFORE THE NEXT REPORTING PERIOD: ENTER THE CONTEXT QUANTITY (0-99999999), FOR EXAMPLE "20".

Name: TOTAL DUE OUT
Explanation: ENTER THE QUANTITY OF ITEMS EXPECTED TO BE TRANSFERRED/DELIVERED OUT OF THE FORMATION/UNIT BEFORE THE NEXT REPORTING PERIOD (NOT CONSUMPTION): ENTER THE CONTEXT QUANTITY (0-99999999), FOR EXAMPLE "5".

Name: ACTUAL ON HAND
Explanation: ENTER THE QUANTITY OF ITEMS PHYSICALLY HELD ON HAND BY FORMATION/UNIT (FOR NATIONAL REPLIES: ON-HAND HOLDINGS PLUS RESERVES) AS FOLLOWS: ENTER THE CONTEXT QUANTITY (0-99999999), FOR EXAMPLE "85".
